Which are the driving factors of the Consumer Internet of Things (IoT) market?
The growth of the Consumer Internet of Things (IoT) market is driven by technological advancements that improve product efficiency and user experience, increasing consumer demand fueled by changing lifestyle preferences, and favorable government regulations and policies that promote market growth. Additionally, growing investments in research and development, along with the expanding application of Consumer IoT across various industries, further accelerate market expansion.
